+
+    Args:
+        cp_chunk_seq_lens_lst: chunk context lengths under CP.
+        origin_context_lens: origin full context lengths under CP.
+        cp_world_size: CP size.
+        sum_seq_len: the sum of cp_chunk_seq_lens_lst.
